{"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/Usage","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LocalNode","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/CreatingNetwork","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/ProvisioningDevices","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/Connecting","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/SendingMessages","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/Configuration","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/Exporting"],"anchor":"Articles","generated":true,"title":"Articles"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The Bluetooth Mesh specification defines DFU starting with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/www.bluetooth.com\/specifications\/specs\/mesh-device-firmware-update-model\/","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Roles","text":"Roles"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Three roles participate in a firmware update over a Bluetooth mesh network:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Initiator","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Initiates the firmware update process.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Distributor"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Receives the firmware and distributes it to Target Nodes."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Target Node"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Receives and applies the firmware update."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A node may perform multiple roles simultaneously — for example, a node can act as both an Initiator and a Distributor."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Firmware-Transfer","text":"Firmware Transfer","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the Mesh DFU specification, there are two methods by which a Distributor can receive the firmware image before distributing it to Target Nodes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"BLOB Transfer"}]},{"type":"text","text":" from the Initiator."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Out-of-Band (OOB)","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" download via HTTPS or other external sources."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"While BLOB Transfer is used for distributing firmware from the Distributor to Target Nodes, it is relatively slow and therefore not suitable for transferring firmware to the Distributor itself."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The second method relies on the Distributor’s ability to download the firmware from the Internet or other external sources.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":4,"anchor":"Simple-Management-Protocol-SMP","text":"Simple Management Protocol (SMP)","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"nRF Mesh","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", a proprietary method using "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Simple Management Protocol (SMP)","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" is employed to transfer firmware from the Initiator to the Distributor. This method is fast and leverages a direct GATT connection instead of Mesh messages."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On the device side, it uses the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/docs.nordicsemi.com\/bundle\/ncs-latest\/page\/zephyr\/services\/device_mgmt\/mcumgr.html"},{"type":"text","text":" with the "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Image","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Shell","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" groups:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Image group"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Transfers the firmware image."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Shell group","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Creates image slots for the firmware."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The app uses the "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/NordicSemiconductor\/IOS-nRF-Connect-Device-Manager\/","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" library to manage SMP transfers."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is recommended to secure the SMP Service on the Distributor using the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/docs.nordicsemi.com\/bundle\/ncs-latest\/page\/nrf\/libraries\/bluetooth\/mesh\/vnd\/le_pair_resp.html","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"vendor model by Nordic Semiconductor. This model provides a Passkey over mesh messages to bond the phone with the Distributor node,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"ensuring that only clients with the correct Network and Application Keys can access the service.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"See more in the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/docs.nordicsemi.com\/bundle\/ncs-latest\/page\/nrf\/samples\/bluetooth\/mesh\/dfu\/distributor\/README.html#smp_over_bluetooth_authentication","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" documentation."}]}]},{"text":"Process","type":"heading","anchor":"Process","level":2},{"text":"1. Bind models to an Application Key","type":"heading","anchor":"1-Bind-models-to-an-Application-Key","level":4},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Ensure the following models are bound to a selected Application Key:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Firmware Distributor Server"},{"type":"text","text":" on the Distributor"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"Firmware Update Client","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" on the Distributor"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"BLOB Transfer Client","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" on the Distributor","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"LE Pairing Responder","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" on the Distributor (if applicable)","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Firmware Update Server"},{"text":" on each Target Node","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"BLOB Transfer Server","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" on each Target Node","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"text":"2. Connect to the Distributor as a GATT Proxy","type":"heading","anchor":"2-Connect-to-the-Distributor-as-a-GATT-Proxy","level":4},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Ensure that the Distributor has the ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"GATT Proxy"}]},{"text":" feature enabled.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Currently, the only supported way to transfer firmware to the Distributor is via the "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SMP Service"}]},{"type":"text","text":". This service can be verified by scanning available GATT services using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CBCentralManager"},{"type":"text","text":" and checking for the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/docs.nordicsemi.com\/bundle\/ncs-latest\/page\/zephyr\/services\/device_mgmt\/smp_transport.html"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"name":"Note","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the SMP Service requires authentication, enabling notifications may trigger a bonding process."},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"text","text":"Before enabling notifications, read the value from the LE Pairing Responder model and present the received "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Passkey"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" to the user."}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":4,"text":"3. Read Distribution Capabilities and Status","anchor":"3-Read-Distribution-Capabilities-and-Status"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Send "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/FirmwareDistributionCapabilitiesGet","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/FirmwareDistributionGet","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" messages to the Distributor to query its capabilities and current state."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This step is optional but recommended to ensure the Distributor is ready and has sufficient storage space."}]},{"type":"heading","level":4,"text":"4. Select Target Nodes and Validate Firmware Metadata","anchor":"4-Select-Target-Nodes-and-Validate-Firmware-Metadata"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Prepare the firmware image and validate it using the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"FirmwareUpdateFirmwareMetadataCheck"},{"type":"text","text":" message."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This validation ensures the firmware is compatible with the selected Target Nodes. It also returns the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/docs.nordicsemi.com\/bundle\/ncs-latest\/page\/zephyr\/connectivity\/bluetooth\/api\/mesh\/dfu.html#firmware_effect","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the update, including whether a node may be unprovisioned post-update (see "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/FirmwareUpdateFirmwareMetadataStatus\/additionalInformation"},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},{"level":4,"anchor":"5-Add-Receivers","text":"5. Add Receivers","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Send the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/FirmwareDistributionReceiversAdd","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" message to the Distributor with the list of Target Nodes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If necessary, clear previous receivers first by sending "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/FirmwareDistributionReceiversDeleteAll"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":4,"anchor":"6-Create-a-Slot-for-the-Firmware-Image","text":"6. Create a Slot for the Firmware Image","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use the Distributor’s ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Shell group"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" over SMP to add a firmware slot:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["let transport = McuMgrBleTransport(gattBearer.identifier)","let shellManager = ShellManager(transport: transport)","shellManager.logDelegate = self","","shellManager.execute(command: \"mesh models dfu slot add \\(image.data.count) \\(firmwareId) \\(metadata)\") { response, error in","    if let text = response?.output,","       let match = text.range(of: #\"Index:\\s*(\\d+)\"#, options: .regularExpression),","       let number = Int(String(text[match]).components(separatedBy: \":\").last?.trimmingCharacters(in: .whitespacesAndNewlines) ?? \"\") {","        let slot = UInt16(truncatingIfNeeded: number)","        \/\/ Use this slot index in the next step.","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This is the only step requiring the Shell interface. If the image is sent via BLOB Transfer (not SMP), the slot is created automatically.","type":"text"}]}],"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Note"},{"level":4,"anchor":"7-Upload-the-Firmware-Image","text":"7. Upload the Firmware Image","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Upload the firmware using the Image Manager:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["let imageManager = ImageManager(transport: transport)","imageManager.logDelegate = self","_ = imageManager.upload(images: [image], using: config, delegate: callback)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Refer to "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/nordicsemi\/IOS-nRF-Mesh-Library\/blob\/main\/Example\/Source\/View%20Controllers\/Network\/DFU\/DFUViewController.swift","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the sample app for a usage example."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":4,"anchor":"8-Start-Firmware-Distribution","text":"8. Start Firmware Distribution","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Initiate distribution by sending the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/FirmwareDistributionStart"},{"text":" message, including the ","type":"text"},{"code":"slot","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" index from step 6 and other DFU parameters.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"9-Apply-the-Firmware-if-verify-only-was-set","level":4,"text":"9. Apply the Firmware (if verify-only was set)","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If the update policy was set to ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/FirmwareUpdatePolicy\/verifyOnly","type":"reference"},{"text":", send ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/FirmwareDistributionApply","type":"reference"},{"text":" to apply the firmware after a successful transfer.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/DFU","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"article","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/dfu"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Updating the firmware of mesh nodes over-the-air (OTA).","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"role":"article","title":"Device Firmware Update"},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh":{"abstract":[{"text":"Provision, configure and control Bluetooth mesh devices with nRF Mesh library.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"NordicMesh","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/FirmwareUpdatePolicy/verifyOnly":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/firmwareupdatepolicy\/verifyonly","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/FirmwareUpdatePolicy\/verifyOnly","title":"FirmwareUpdatePolicy.verifyOnly","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"verifyOnly"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Firmware Distribution Server verifies that firmware image distribution completed"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"successfully but does not apply the update. The Initiator (the Firmware Distribution Client)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"initiates firmware image application."}]},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/Configuration":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/Configuration","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/configuration","title":"Configuration","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Configuration allows to customize the behavior of the local and remote nodes."}],"role":"article"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/Usage":{"role":"article","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/usage","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/Usage","title":"Usage","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"How to start."}]},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/Exporting":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/Exporting","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/exporting","title":"Exporting network configuration","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Export and import feature allows to share mesh network configuration between"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"devices."}],"role":"article"},"https://github.com/NordicSemiconductor/IOS-nRF-Connect-Device-Manager/":{"title":"nRF Connect Device Manager","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/NordicSemiconductor\/IOS-nRF-Connect-Device-Manager\/","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"nRF Connect Device Manager","type":"text"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/NordicSemiconductor\/IOS-nRF-Connect-Device-Manager\/"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/FirmwareDistributionReceiversAdd":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/FirmwareDistributionReceiversAdd","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"FirmwareDistributionReceiversAdd","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/firmwaredistributionreceiversadd","abstract":[{"text":"The Firmware Distribution Receivers Add message is an acknowledged message sent by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a Firmware Distribution Client to add new entries to the Distribution Receivers List state of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a Firmware Distribution Server.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FirmwareDistributionReceiversAdd","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"FirmwareDistributionReceiversAdd","type":"topic"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/FirmwareDistributionStart":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/FirmwareDistributionStart","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/firmwaredistributionstart","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Firmware Distribution Start message is an acknowledged message sent by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a Firmware Distribution Client to start the firmware image distribution to the Target Nodes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the Distribution Receivers List."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"FirmwareDistributionStart"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"FirmwareDistributionStart"}],"title":"FirmwareDistributionStart"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/FirmwareDistributionCapabilitiesGet":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/firmwaredistributioncapabilitiesget","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"FirmwareDistributionCapabilitiesGet"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/FirmwareDistributionCapabilitiesGet","title":"FirmwareDistributionCapabilitiesGet","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"FirmwareDistributionCapabilitiesGet"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Firmware Distribution Capabilities Get message is an acknowledged message sent by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a Firmware Distribution Client to get the capabilities of a Firmware Distribution Server."}]},"https://docs.nordicsemi.com/bundle/ncs-latest/page/nrf/libraries/bluetooth/mesh/vnd/le_pair_resp.html":{"type":"link","url":"https:\/\/docs.nordicsemi.com\/bundle\/ncs-latest\/page\/nrf\/libraries\/bluetooth\/mesh\/vnd\/le_pair_resp.html","identifier":"https:\/\/docs.nordicsemi.com\/bundle\/ncs-latest\/page\/nrf\/libraries\/bluetooth\/mesh\/vnd\/le_pair_resp.html","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"LE Pairing Responder"}]}],"title":"LE Pairing Responder"},"https://docs.nordicsemi.com/bundle/ncs-latest/page/nrf/samples/bluetooth/mesh/dfu/distributor/README.html#smp_over_bluetooth_authentication":{"title":"SMP over Bluetooth authentication","url":"https:\/\/docs.nordicsemi.com\/bundle\/ncs-latest\/page\/nrf\/samples\/bluetooth\/mesh\/dfu\/distributor\/README.html#smp_over_bluetooth_authentication","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SMP over Bluetooth authentication"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/docs.nordicsemi.com\/bundle\/ncs-latest\/page\/nrf\/samples\/bluetooth\/mesh\/dfu\/distributor\/README.html#smp_over_bluetooth_authentication"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/SendingMessages":{"kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/SendingMessages","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/sendingmessages","abstract":[{"text":"How to send mesh messages using the manager.","type":"text"}],"role":"article","title":"Sending messages"},"https://docs.nordicsemi.com/bundle/ncs-latest/page/zephyr/services/device_mgmt/mcumgr.html":{"title":"Management subsystem","url":"https:\/\/docs.nordicsemi.com\/bundle\/ncs-latest\/page\/zephyr\/services\/device_mgmt\/mcumgr.html",